name: Laser Quartz // (60 g/mol - 2.660)
description: Natural formed Laser Quartz is a powerful healing tool that needs purity of intent. It focuses, concentrates, and accelerates energy into a tight beam that is suitable for psychic surgery, stimulating acupuncture points, and reaching tiny structures deep within the body. Prized for millennia as a worker of magic and a potent shamanic tool. Generating electromagnetism, dispelling static electricity, it is an extremely powerful healing and energy amplifier. Laser Quartz cuts away negativity, inappropriate attitudes, outmoded though patterns, and energy blockages.
